value_i18n.ar_SA:
Register Now: September Liferay Learning Paths

This September, empower your team members (Customer Facing, Business Sales, and Technical Pre-Sales) through role-based learning paths to position and sell Liferay.  

Important to know

  • Browse the Learning Path topics below to see the list of sessions by role. The live webinars will be presented twice as Session A and Session B.
  • Content for sessions A and B are identical, so join the session that best fits your schedule in your preferred time zone.
  • Choose only Session A or only Session B and click the session link to complete your registration. The agenda and session duration for individual sessions are displayed on the registration page.
  • Use your business email to register as a Liferay partner.
  • Reach out to partner-enablement@liferay.com with any questions.
